_sText:
Fixed a problem with the boosters, re-download the map if you downloaded it within a few minutes after it was uploaded or played the test version.

A short map intended for speedrunning.

I started making this map in order to try out a new 1-hop trigger system I invented which didn't work out (changed to mpbhops), hence the blocks being positioned the way they are. I think some areas could've used some additional detailing, but I don't feel like spending any more time on it. Comes with a bonus and some secrets.
